avahi: Avahi - Local network service discovery
avahi:
avahi: Avahi is an implementation of the Multicast DNS and DNS Service
avahi: Discovery (mDNS/DNS-SD) specifications for Zeroconf computing.
avahi: This means that you can plug your machine into a network and instantly
avahi: be able to view other people whom you can chat with, find printers to
avahi: print to, or find files being shared. This kind of technology is
avahi: already found in MacOS X (also known as Rendezvous, Bonjour, and
avahi: Zeroconf). It is based on the discontinued flexmdns project.
avahi:
avahi: Packaged by Georgi D. Sotirov <gdsotirov@gmail.com>
